  <brief_title>High-sensitivity C-reactive Protein and United Kingdom Prospective Diabetes Study (UKPDS) Risk Score in Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>High-sensitivity C-reactive Protein and UKPDS Risk Score in Type 2 Diabetes: Nalysis With 18F-Fluorodeoxyglucose Positron Emission Tomography</official_title>
